~ start
if !GameManager.check_flag(ID)
	do GameManager.set_flag(ID, true)
	Discovered Elevator {{ID}}!
Get on the elevator?
- Use
	=> elevatorEnter
- Leave
=> END

~ elevatorEnter
do enter_elevator()
=> END

~ creator
???: Welcome to my elevator room.
???: I, am the creator of the elevator.
???: With my glorious creation, I may travel the world at my leisure.
???: Please try out my elevator when you have a chance.